L -RRB- Chief Executive Bob Dudley has stepped up his battle to rebuild the troubled oil giant 's reputation , declaring safety is so core to the group that it would be the sole measure for staff bonuses in <TIMEX3 tid="t6" type="DATE" value="2010-Q4">the last quarter of this year</TIMEX3> .
Dudley needs to restore investor confidence in the oil group following its Gulf of Mexico oil spill and other disasters in <TIMEX3 tid="t9" type="DATE" value="PAST_REF">recent years</TIMEX3> , and to fend off threats to BP 's ability to operate in the United States .
