Dudley disputes this claim and to emphasize BP 's commitment to safety he told staff in an email , seen by Reuters , that : ` ` The sole criterion for performance reward for our operating businesses in <TIMEX3 tid="t14" type="DATE" value="2010-Q4">the fourth quarter of 2010</TIMEX3> will be performance in safety , compliance , silent running and operational risk management . ''
` ` We are taking this step in order to be absolutely clear that safety , compliance and operational risk management is BP 's number one priority , well ahead of all other priorities , '' he added in the email which was sent on <TIMEX3 tid="t17" type="DATE" value="2010-10-18">Monday</TIMEX3> .
